	<title>Report State View</title>

	<section>

		<para>The Report State view moves to the front when a report is executed. This view shows:
		</para>
		<itemizedlist mark='opencircle'>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					The console which displays the report execution process in real-time.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					A list of errors that occurs during report execution. Double clicking an error will open error dialog with a detailed stacktrace.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Some statistics of report execution like fill size, record count, page count, compilation time, filling time, export time.
				</para>
			</listitem>

		</itemizedlist>

		<figure>
			<title>Report State View</title>
			<screenshot>
				<mediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="reportstate.png" format="PNG" />
					</imageobject>
				</mediaobject>
			</screenshot>
		</figure>

	</section>

</section>